    "name": "Resource Allocation API",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for Resource Allocation System API\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1\n\n===========================\nSEED DATA (V2__seed_data.sql) - lần chạy Flyway đầu tiên\n===========================\n--- Employee ---\nEMP001: Nguyen Van A, Java Developer  - 100% allocated (PRJ001=60%, PRJ002=40%)\nEMP002: Tran Thi B,  Java Developer   -  80% allocated (PRJ001=80%)\nEMP003: Le Van C,    React Developer  -  40% allocated (PRJ001=40%)\nEMP004: Pham Van D,  DevOps Engineer  -   0% allocated\n\n--- Project ---\nPRJ001: E-Commerce Platform,  ACTIVE\nPRJ002: Internal Dashboard,   PLANNING\nPRJ003: Legacy Upgrade,       COMPLETED\n\n--- Allocation ---\nEMP001(60%) -> PRJ001  |  EMP001(40%) -> PRJ002\nEMP002(80%) -> PRJ001  |  EMP003(40%) -> PRJ001\n\n⚠️ ID là BIGSERIAL tự tăng.\nNếu DB đã chạy nhiều lần, ID KHÔNG còn là 1,2,3...\n→ Test scripts không assert cứng ID, chỉ assert cấu trúc + status code.\n→ URL mẫu vẫn dùng /1, /2,... nhưng hãy thay bằng ID thực tế nếu test sai.",
